## Prep Status — Full Lifecycle

```
created (prepping)
    ↓
agent running (prepping — steps logged)
    ↓
  ┌─ agent needs input → clarifying (prepping — waiting for user reply)
  │       ↓ user replies
  └─────────────────────┘
    ↓
quality check passes → ready
    ↓
user acts → archived

at any point:
    → failed (logged, stays visible to user with retry option)
```

