## Build Checklist — Core Loop

The core loop is not done until all of these pass:

```
□ POST /dumps returns in < 200ms regardless of how many thoughts
□ SSE connection established before first prep.created event
□ Prep cards appear on confirmation screen as they are created
□ Prep cards transition from prepping → ready without full refresh
□ App open with cached data shows instantly — no empty state flash
□ Skeleton cards show when no cache exists
□ Background sync on app foreground is silent
□ Options results have real names, real prices, real URLs
□ Agent steps are all logged to agent_steps table
□ Failed preps show retry option — not a blank card
□ Push notification fires when all preps for a dump are ready
□ stream.done fires after last prep settles
□ SSE connection closes after stream.done
□ Clarify flow pauses job, resumes on user reply
□ Profile is updated after every prep with new facts learned
```

